<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Website</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* BANNER */
        .banner {
            width: 100%;
            height: 400px;
            background-color: #cccccc;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .banner img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        /* NAVIGATION */
        nav {
            background-color: #222;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* MAIN CONTENT */
        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .intro-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* SECTIONS WITH SIDE IMAGES */
        .section {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .section.reverse {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }

        .section-image {
            width: 300px;
            min-width: 300px;
            height: 220px;
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .section-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .section-text h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: #222;
        }

        .section-text p {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* FOOTER */
        footer {
            background-color: #222;
            color: #aaa;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 60px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- NAVIGATION -->
    <nav>
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">About</a>
        <a href="#">Services</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <!-- BANNER IMAGE -->
    <!-- Replace "your-banner-image.jpg" with your image file name -->
    <div class="banner">
        <img src="your-banner-image.jpg" alt="Banner Image">
    </div>

    <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
    <div class="container">

        <h1>Welcome to My Website</h1>
        <p class="intro-text">This is a short introduction to your website. Describe what you do, what this site is about, or what visitors can expect to find here.</p>

        <!-- SECTION 1 - image on the left -->
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-image">
                <!-- Replace "your-image-1.jpg" with your image file name -->
                <img src="your-image-1.jpg" alt="Section 1 Image">
            </div>
            <div class="section-text">
                <h2>First Subheadline</h2>
                <p>Write your content here. This could be a description of a product, a service, a story, or anything you want to share. Keep it clear and easy to read.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SECTION 2 - image on the right -->
        <div class="section reverse">
            <div class="section-image">
                <!-- Replace "your-image-2.jpg" with your image file name -->
                <img src="your-image-2.jpg" alt="Section 2 Image">
            </div>
            <div class="section-text">
                <h2>Second Subheadline</h2>
                <p>Write your content here. You can describe another topic, feature, or idea. Each section alternates the image side to keep the layout interesting.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SECTION 3 - image on the left -->
        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-image">
                <!-- Replace "your-image-3.jpg" with your image file name -->
                <img src="your-image-3.jpg" alt="Section 3 Image">
            </div>
            <div class="section-text">
                <h2>Third Subheadline</h2>
                <p>Write your content here. Add as many sections as you need by copying the section block above and swapping out the image and text.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 My Website. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
